## 1. Purpose

Turn HR134's route-agreement classification into a standing law-mining instrument: a registry of certified route-equivalence laws with region guards, plus the intake machinery that promotes observed agreement into law or confirms it coincidental. The registry STORES and CERTIFIES laws; it never applies them (application is certified-form-synthesis territory).

